        "/\\.mozilla/firefox/[^/]+/(logins\\.json|logins-backup\\.json|key4\\.db|key3\\.db)$"
      ],
      "description": "Firefox profile saved-passwords surface: logins.json holds encrypted login records, key4.db / key3.db are the NSS key databases that decrypt them. Either file alone is high-value; pair recovered = cleartext recovery. Windows AppData and Linux dotdir profiles both covered. Closes Snaffler #46."
    },
    {
      "rule_name": "ShareSiftKeepGppPolicyXml",
      "triage": "Black",
